The Resolution: 4.d3 wins.
The Reasoning: 4.d3 is far more consistent with your cage setup
. By pairing it with a4 and retreating your bishop to Ba2, you elegantly neutralize Black's ...Na5 queenside expansion while keeping your most valuable bishop safe on its active diagonal
